  "keyFeatures": [
    "Real-time FNC coffee price scraping (Mon–Fri, 8am & 1pm Bogotá time) with NY futures fallback",
    "Hybrid ML price prediction model combining Prophet, XGBoost, naive, and formula-based strategies",
    "Interactive buyer map showing coffee buyers across Huila municipalities with approximate coordinates",
    "Role-based access control: producer (caficultor), buyer (comprador), and admin roles",
    "Configurable price threshold alerts with email notifications for producers",
    "AI-powered news aggregation and auto-generation via OpenAI + multiple news APIs",
    "Kaffi chatbot assistant powered by OpenAI for user guidance",
    "Google OAuth + JWT authentication with email verification",
    "GitHub Actions workflow for automated daily ML pipeline execution",
    "Deployable on Railway (backend) + Netlify (frontend)"
  ],
